    "posthog_status": "Backend POSTHOG_API_KEY was not yet set on staging deploy when these runs were captured. Per-iteration / per-run events therefore did not arrive in PostHog for these specific runs. Frontend bench_appevent_run_triggered events did arrive (frontend uses posthog-js with its own config). Subsequent runs after env var is set will populate PostHog."
  },

